# 🗂️ 2. Database Design (Schema Structure)

## 2.1 License Types Table

Stores all available license/agreement categories.

**Table: `license_types`**

| Field       | Type     | Description                       |
| ----------- | -------- | --------------------------------- |
| id          | INT (PK) | Unique ID                         |
| name        | VARCHAR  | e.g., Rent Agreement, Food Safety |
| description | TEXT     | Optional notes                    |
| created_at  | DATETIME | Timestamp                         |
| updated_at  | DATETIME | Timestamp                         |

---

## 2.2 Clients Table (If already exists, extend it)

**Table: `clients`**

| Field      | Type     |
| ---------- | -------- |
| id         | INT (PK) |
| name       | VARCHAR  |
| email      | VARCHAR  |
| phone      | VARCHAR  |
| address    | TEXT     |
| created_at | DATETIME |

---

## 2.3 Client License Records

This connects clients with specific licenses.

**Table: `client_licenses`**

| Field           | Type                            | Description |
| --------------- | ------------------------------- | ----------- |
| id              | INT (PK)                        |             |
| client_id       | FK → clients.id                 |             |
| license_type_id | FK → license_types.id           |             |
| file_no         | VARCHAR                         |             |
| service_date    | DATE                            |             |
| expiry_date     | DATE                            |             |
| status          | ENUM (Active, Expired, Renewed) |             |
| notes           | TEXT                            |             |
| created_at      | DATETIME                        |             |
| updated_at      | DATETIME                        |             |

---

## 2.4 Services Table (Optional Enhancement)

If each license has service details:

**Table: `services`**

| Field               | Type     |
| ------------------- | -------- |
| id                  | INT (PK) |
| client_license_id   | FK       |
| service_description | TEXT     |
| service_cost        | DECIMAL  |
| service_date        | DATE     |

