## 2.5 Billing Table

**Table: `billing`**

| Field             | Type                 |
| ----------------- | -------------------- |
| id                | INT                  |
| client_license_id | FK                   |
| amount            | DECIMAL              |
| payment_status    | ENUM (Paid, Pending) |
| invoice_no        | VARCHAR              |
| payment_date      | DATE                 |

---

## 2.6 Notifications Table

**Table: `notifications`**

| Field             | Type                   |
| ----------------- | ---------------------- |
| id                | INT                    |
| client_license_id | FK                     |
| notification_type | ENUM (Expiry Reminder) |
